{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"917856449b","title":"大字报诗——回顾","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e35bc6bcb6","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"917856449b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"222c241b8a","name":"成都工学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"739081cc10","type":"title","text":"大字报诗——回顾","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"db67849203","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"abcabccd7c","type":"subtitle","text":"（原著名“鸣者”，为成都工学院学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"605f6b4d1c","type":"paragraph","text":"我忧伤，我沉郁，看着我们这一代的人！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"9d0d4054d1","type":"paragraph","text":"从老年、青年至少年的灵魂","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"af8ddca270","type":"paragraph","text":"人人都说着同一的话语，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"e2e85e86d9","type":"paragraph","text":"重复着千篇一律的声音，而平淡，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"26faa0dd1c","type":"paragraph","text":"单调，无为生活，也就苦磨着我们！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"19d7e45c0f","type":"paragraph","text":"象蠋虫一样在认识与怀疑的重压下","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"d9ac80074b","type":"paragraph","text":"触目惊心，冷冷默默的爬行，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"97aad0adad","type":"paragraph","text":"虽然生活给我们展示了美好的远景，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"acdfc4a7bb","type":"paragraph","text":"而我们都作了物质的奴隶，冷冰的机械人，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"10a6919662","type":"paragraph","text":"我们希望过、描画过、渴求过，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"325e860e50","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么丰饶的智慧，热情的冲动，诗的灵感和幻想，艺术的才能和创造，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"f563423415","type":"paragraph","text":"很快的就暗淡了，沉默了，哑口无言！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"c60ec97a53","type":"paragraph","text":"难道大自然有这般魔力，能把温郁沉闷冷漠的画笔，无情地渲染，给我们颜色。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"05b68aabda","type":"paragraph","text":"我们才迎来黎明的曙光(正欲举步前行)","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"989adabac7","type":"paragraph","text":"又飘来来一片惨淡的愁云，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"5fe588f4cb","type":"paragraph","text":"在教条束缚的迷雾下，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"7a9ad728c4","type":"paragraph","text":"在宗派森严的官墙下，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"9cf7c23bde","type":"paragraph","text":"不必的警惕和怀疑代替了友谊和信任，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"02453d7320","type":"paragraph","text":"冷漠和虚伪掩盖了真实的感情，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"6ff88e843d","type":"paragraph","text":"一丝淡漠的浅笑，我们也交朋友，也去看别人！","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"b514c4d323","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不止一次地述说着，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"ad63d6b3f8","type":"paragraph","text":"传(？)播着自欺欺人的诺言，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"217eb5f9cb","type":"paragraph","text":"而心灵遣责我们！","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"0991536742","type":"paragraph","text":"良心控诉我们！","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"9d154edd58","type":"paragraph","text":"我们还要强调地说，“这就是真理”","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"1de11048d6","type":"paragraph","text":"虽然我们也曾感到内心悲痛和挣扎！","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"359200c454","type":"paragraph","text":"但，我在命运的海洋里，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"4252e7a309","type":"paragraph","text":"惊涛起伏、骇浪翻滚！","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"9d7bf179ef","type":"paragraph","text":"人们已经习惯了善伪其浮沉！","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"},{"id":"b8f9bae138","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《四川省右派言论选辑4》(内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印)，中共四川省委宣传部办公室编，1957年7月28日。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b"}],"page":{"id":"0be628dbd0","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"917856449b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}